openapi: 3.0.3
info:
  title: ''

        - JSON: application/vnd.oai.openapi+json

      tags:
      - api
      security:
      - cookieAuth: []
      - basicAuth: []
      - {}
      responses:
        '200':
          content:
            application/vnd.oai.openapi:
              schema:
                type: object
                additionalProperties: {}
            application/yaml:
              schema:
                type: object
                additionalProperties: {}
            application/vnd.oai.openapi+json:
              schema:

                additionalProperties: {}
            application/json:
              schema:

          description: ''
  /chef/pizza:
    get:
      operationId: chef_pizza_list
      tags:
      - chef
      responses:
        '200':
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                type: array
                items:
                  $ref: '#/components/schemas/Pizza'
          description: ''
  /chef/pizza/{id}:
    put:
      operationId: chef_pizza_update
      parameters:
      - in: path
        name: id
        schema:
          type: integer
        required: true
      tags:
      - chef
      requestBody:
        content:
          application/json:
            schema:
              $ref: '#/components/schemas/Pizza'
          application/x-www-form-urlencoded:
            schema:
              $ref: '#/components/schemas/Pizza'
          multipart/form-data:
            schema:
              $ref: '#/components/schemas/Pizza'
        required: true
      security:
      - cookieAuth: []
      - basicAuth: []
      - {}
      responses:
        '200':
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/Pizza'
          description: ''
    patch:
      operationId: chef_pizza_partial_update

      - in: path
        name: id
        schema:
          type: integer
        required: true
      tags:

      requestBody:
        content:
          application/json:
            schema:
              $ref: '#/components/schemas/PatchedPizza'
          application/x-www-form-urlencoded:
            schema:
              $ref: '#/components/schemas/PatchedPizza'
          multipart/form-data:
            schema:
              $ref: '#/components/schemas/PatchedPizza'
      security:
      - cookieAuth: []
      - basicAuth: []
      - {}
      responses:
        '200':
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/Pizza'
          description: ''
  /chef/pizza/{id}/delete:
    delete:
      operationId: chef_pizza_delete_destroy
      parameters:
      - in: path
        name: id
        schema:
          type: integer
        required: true
      tags:
      - chef
      security:
      - cookieAuth: []
      - basicAuth: []
      - {}
      responses:
        '204':
          description: No response body
  /chef/pizza/create:
    post:
      operationId: chef_pizza_create_create
      tags:

      parameters:
      - in: path
        name: id
        schema:
          type: integer
        required: true
      tags:

      security:
      - cookieAuth: []
      - basicAuth: []
      - {}
      responses:

  /owner/toppings/create:
    post:
      operationId: owner_toppings_create_create
      tags:

      requestBody:
        content:

          application/x-www-form-urlencoded:

      - basicAuth: []
      - {}

          description: ''
  /owner/toppings/view/{id}:
    get:
      operationId: owner_toppings_view_retrieve
      parameters:
      - in: path
        name: id
        schema:
          type: integer
        required: true
      tags:

      security:

      - {}

components:
  schemas:
    PatchedPizza:
      type: object
      properties:
        id:
          type: integer
          readOnly: true
        name:
          type: string
          maxLength: 60
        toppings:
          type: array
          items:
            type: integer
    PatchedToppings:
      type: object
      properties:
        id:
          type: integer
          readOnly: true
        name:
          type: string
          maxLength: 60
    Pizza:
      type: object
      properties:
        id:
          type: integer
          readOnly: true
        name:
          type: string
          maxLength: 60
        toppings:
          type: array
          items:
            type: integer
      required:
      - id
      - name
      - toppings
    Toppings:
      type: object
      properties:
        id:
          type: integer
          readOnly: true
        name:
          type: string
          maxLength: 60
      required:
      - id
      - name
  securitySchemes:
    basicAuth:
      type: http
      scheme: basic
    cookieAuth:
      type: apiKey
      in: cookie
      name: sessionid
